def transform_dataset(input_list):
    output_list = []
    temp_record = []

    for item in input_list:
        if item == ['']:
            if temp_record:
                output_list.append(temp_record)
                temp_record = []
        else:
            temp_record.extend(item)

    if temp_record:
        output_list.append(temp_record)

    return output_list
